attributes.description: Sunrise across Principal Valley to signify a new light and journey
Exposure to the red arid soil of the Bullish Valleys has made the skin of each new generation become slightly more pink
This tight-fitting outfit is reserved for night-time missions, as sunlight tends to damage leather. It gives off a particular shine, as if emitting its own light
Long hair worn worn loosely as if unconcerned with worldly matters. Green like the spoils of a fresh harvest
A smile conveys a world of meaning, yet its meaning isn’t always certain
Elves are a naturally inquisitive lot, always doing their own research, skeptical of tall tales
Eyes as gold as sunlight convey friendliness, but don’t mistake it for complacency
Headwear is reserved for those with the means and desire to show off
No need for eyewear, adventure is afoot
Battle mask covering the wearer's mouth, it enhances oxygen intake and fearsomeness
